trans-unit.source: Indicates how a <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Animation.ParallelTimeline"></xref> will behave when one or more of its <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline"></xref> children slips.
trans-unit.target: 指示如何<xref href="System.Windows.Media.Animation.ParallelTimeline"></xref>时的行为一个或多个其<xref href="System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline"></xref>子级滑动。

trans-unit.source: Indicates that a <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Animation.ParallelTimeline"></xref> will not slip with the child <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline"></xref>, but will expand to fit all slipping <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline"></xref> children.
trans-unit.target: 指示<xref href="System.Windows.Media.Animation.ParallelTimeline"></xref>不会随子落后<xref href="System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline"> </xref>，但将扩展以适应所有滑动<xref href="System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline"></xref>子级。

trans-unit.source: **NOTE**: This is only effective when the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline.Duration*> of the <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Animation.ParallelTimeline"></xref> is not explicitly specified.
trans-unit.target: **请注意**︰ 这有效时才<xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline.Duration*>的<xref href="System.Windows.Media.Animation.ParallelTimeline"></xref>未显式指定。</xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline.Duration*>

trans-unit.source: Indicates that a <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Animation.ParallelTimeline"></xref> will slip along with its first child <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline"></xref> that can slip whenever that child is delayed or accelerated..
trans-unit.target: 指示<xref href="System.Windows.Media.Animation.ParallelTimeline"></xref>将沿其第一个子级<xref href="System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline"></xref>延迟或加速该子级时，就可以绕...
